Name: Fraser
Description:
The Division of Fraser consists of:

  • part of the Brimbank City Council, and
  • part of the Maribyrnong City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Manufacturing, wholesale trade, construction, transport and warehousing, retail trade, health care and education. Major industrial areas are located in the eastern and southern parts of the division.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of the Rt Hon. John Malcom Fraser AC CH, 1930-2015. Fraser was Prime Minister of Australia (1975-83) and a Member of the House of Representatives (1955-83).
Members: The first member for Fraser will be elected at the next federal general election.
DemographicRating: Outer Metropolitan - situated in capital cities and containing large areas of recent suburban expansion.
